# Zombie Forest Shooter

Game shooter survival berbasis web menggunakan **Phaser 3 + TypeScript + Vite**.

---

# 🎮 Features

- WASD movement
- Mouse aiming
- Auto shooting
- Dash movement
- Enemy zombie AI
- Procedural forest background
- HP system
- Score system
- Game over system
- Camera shake & recoil
- Bullet trail effect
- Responsive fullscreen

---

# 🕹 Controls

| Action | Key |
|---|---|
| Move | WASD |
| Shoot | Hold Left Click |
| Dash | SPACE |
| Restart | R |

---

# 🛠 Tech Stack

- Phaser 3
- TypeScript
- Vite

---

# 📦 Installation

## Clone repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/USERNAME/shooter-game.git
```

## Masuk folder project

```bash
cd shooter-game
```

## Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

## Jalankan development server

```bash
npm run dev
```

---

# 🚀 Build Production

```bash
npm run build
```

---

# 📁 Project Structure

```txt
shooter-game/
├── public/
│   └── assets/
│       ├── player.png
│       ├── enemy.png
│       └── bullet.png
│
├── src/
│   ├── scenes/
│   │   └── MainScene.ts
│   │
│   └── main.ts
│
├── package.json
├── vite.config.ts
└── README.md
```

---

# 🎨 Assets

Masukkan asset ke folder:

```txt
public/assets/
```

Required assets:

- player.png
- enemy.png
- bullet.png

---

# 🌲 Gameplay

Bertahan hidup selama mungkin dari serangan zombie di hutan.

- Enemy akan terus spawn
- Semakin tinggi score, enemy semakin cepat
- Gunakan dash untuk menghindar
- Kalah jika HP habis

